{"type":"item.completed","item":{"id":"item_113","type":"agent_message","text":"I’ve confirmed the JLine loader extracts `libjlinenative.so` from the jar and calls `System.load` on that extracted file before `CLibrary$Termios.<clinit>` invokes the native `init()`. Next I’m checking whether the newer `3.30.7` fixture fails the same way and whether `jline-native` itself already demonstrates a working future-defaults path that `jline-terminal-jni` can reuse."}}
